#include <cstdio>
#include <cstring>
char buf[104];
int main(){
	//scanf("%s", buf);
	int c=0;
	char t;
	while ((t=getchar()) != EOF){
		buf[c++]=t;
	}
	buf[t++]=0;
	int len = strlen(buf);
	putchar(buf[0]);
	for (int i=1; i<len; i++){
		if (buf[i]==' ' && buf[i-1]==' ') continue;
		putchar(buf[i]);
	}
	return 0;
}
